            "body": "Isn't this already possible using the {{-shell_env}} CLI option?  Are you proposing adding in a switch, like {{-docker <image>}}, that would encapsulate setting {{-shell_env YARN_CONTAINER_RUNTIME_TYPE=docker -shell_env YARN_CONTAINER_RUNTIME_DOCKER_IMAGE=<image>}}?",
